    "Brand reputation risk if partner experiences quality or PR issues"
  ],
  "open_questions": [
    "Should we pursue exclusive partnerships or allow multiple partners in same category?",
    "What is our minimum partner revenue threshold to justify dedicated support resources?",
    "How do we handle channel conflict if partner competes with our direct sales?",
    "What decision authority does partnerships team have without executive approval?"
  ]
}
